data.description: Price Reduced to $249,900! Beautifully freshened and well maintained town home located in the prestigious Fort Dodge Country Club. Walking in you will notice the brightly lit interior, newer flooring, fresh paint, and the newly remodeled kitchen with updated lighting that is fit for a chef. When spring rolls around you will also benefit from the meticulous landscaping and generous entertaining areas with over 600 sq of deck and patio area. You will not have to worry about any pesky HOA dues or minimums to the Country Club either. Call Scott at 515-571-2761 or MIke at 515-573-9335 to view today.
